Titolo: House of the Dying Sun

Anno: 2016

Descrizione: House of the Dying Sun, formerly Enemy Starfighter, is an action video game developed and published by Marauder Interactive. It was released on November 2, 2016 for Microsoft Windows and went through Steam's Early Access program prior to its full release. The game features optional virtual reality options that work with the HTC Vive and the Oculus Rift. The game contains fourteen scenarios that the player is able to complete, with the gameplay consisting of both first-person "cockpit combat" and an overlay in which the player is able to assume control of or give orders to ships in their fleet.

Genere: Action 

Valutazione: N/A
